{
  "text": "Five studies analysed both measures of physical activity and overweight [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] including one study which considered additionally mental and physical quality of life, and depressive symptoms [CITATION_6] . One of these studies used data from students aged 13-16 years [CITATION_7] .",
